data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-full bathroom ranch-style home, located in Central Dauphin School District. The heart of the home is the tastefully updated kitchen, offering both functionality and style. Two separate living spaces on the main floor provide plenty of space for everyone. Step outside your family room onto your elevated wood deck with steps down to your fully fenced in yard.  The lower level features a large unfinished space perfect for storage or you can finish for even more living space!  This home effortlessly blends comfort with practicality, creating an ideal setting for both daily living and entertaining.
